<item>
            <title>[MATH-844] &quot;HarmonicFitter.ParameterGuesser&quot; sometimes fails to return sensible values</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MATH-844</link>
                <project id="12310485" key="MATH">Commons Math</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The inner class &quot;ParameterGuesser&quot; in &quot;HarmonicFitter&quot; (package &quot;o.a.c.m.optimization.fitting&quot;) fails to compute a usable guess for the &quot;amplitude&quot; parameter.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12603145">MATH-844</key>
            <summary>&quot;HarmonicFitter.ParameterGuesser&quot; sometimes fails to return sensible values</summary>
